ating. Do you like me, like me?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="6757" d="2402" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčWoah, my heart's beating. Do you like me, like me?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="6757" d="2402" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčWoah, my heart's beating. Do you like me, like me?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="9159" d="1936" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčAh... my heart's throbbing. Die, die, die, die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="9159" d="1936" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčAh... my heart's throbbing. Die, die, die, die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="9159" d="1936" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčAh... my heart's throbbing. Die, die, die, die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="11095" d="2369" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčI want that blue ribbon,‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="11095" d="2369" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčI want that blue ribbon,‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="11095" d="2369" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčI want that blue ribbon,‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="13464" d="2536" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčI don't wanna come in second place.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="13464" d="2536" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčI don't wanna come in second place.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="13464" d="2536" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčI don't wanna come in second place.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="16000" d="2535" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčEverybody's parting ways with me cause I'm so annoying.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="16000" d="2535" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčEverybody's parting ways with me cause I'm so annoying.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="16000" d="2535" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčEverybody's parting ways with me cause I'm so annoying.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="18535" d="2636" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčBeing a handful is unpopular. Why? Why? Why?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="18535" d="2636" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčBeing a handful is unpopular. Why? Why? Why?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="18535" d="2636" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčBeing a handful is unpopular. Why? Why? Why?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="21171" d="2503" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčI'm lost. I'm at a loss and I'm feeling lost.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="21171" d="2503" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčI'm lost. I'm at a loss and I'm feeling lost.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="21171" d="2503" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčI'm lost. I'm at a loss and I'm feeling lost.‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="23674" d="2703" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe girl who never gets chosen... I'm gonna die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="23674" d="2703" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe girl who never gets chosen... I'm gonna die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="23674" d="2703" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe girl who never gets chosen... I'm gonna die!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="26377" d="2102" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčPsycho? The psycho is... which, which one?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="26377" d="2102" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="3">‚Äč ‚ÄčPsycho? The psycho is... which, which one?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="26377" d="2102" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="4">‚Äč ‚ÄčPsycho? The psycho is... which, which one?‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="28479" d="2969" wp="1" ws="1"><s p="1">‚Äč</s>‚Äč<s p="2">‚Äč ‚ÄčThe only thing I can believe in... is your face!‚Äč ‚Äč</s><s p="1">‚Äč</s></p><p t="28479" d="2969"